quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  44,19,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,20,"wala ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,21,"wa'alla ttkbru ealaa allah btkdhyb rslh, 'iiniy atikum bbrhan wadih ealaa sidq rsalty, 'iiniy astjrt biallah rabiy warabukum 'ana tqtlwny rjmana balhjart, wa'iin lam tsdqwny ealaa ma jitukum bih fkhllu sbyly, wkffu ean adhay"
  44,22,fdea musaa rbh- hin kadhibuh fireawn waqawmuh walam yuminuu bh- qayla 'iina hwla' qawm mushrikun biallah kafrwn
  44,23,"f'asr- ya mwsa- bebady- aladhin saddaqwk, waminuu bk, watbewk, dun aladhin kadhabuk mnhm- laylana 'iinakum mutabaeun min fireawn wajunuduh ftnjwn, wyghrq fireawn wjnwdh"
  44,24,"watrk albahr kama hu ealaa halatih alty kan ealayha hin slkth, saknana ghyr mdtrb, 'iina fireawn wajunuduh mughraqun fi albhr"
  44,25,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,26,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,27,"km tarak fireawn waqawmuh baed muhlikuhum w'ighraq allah 'iiahum min basatin wajanaat nadrt, waeuyun min alma' jaryt, wazurue wamanazil jmylt, weysht kanuu fiha mtnemyn mtrfyn"
  44,28,"mthl dhlk aleiqab yeaqb allah man kdhdhab wbddal niemat allah kfrana, wa'awrathna tilk alnaeam min baed fireawn waqawmuh qwmana akharin khlfwhm min bani 'israyyl"
  44,29,"fma bakat alsama' wal'ard hznana ealaa fireawn wqwmh, wama kanuu mwkhkharyn ean aleuqubat alty hllat bhm"
  44,30,wlqd njjayna bani 'iisrayiyl min aleadhab almudhll lahum biqatl abnayhm waistikhdam nsayhm
